      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is commercially validated software with documented QA procedures including version control, regression testing, and release notes. SQA level 2 achieved through documented solver validation suite and traceable version records."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
